Join in on the fun at Suncoast Casino, Hotels and Entertainment with Open Air Salsa every month. Free, fun and suitable for the entire family, Open Air Salsa are dance lessons in the South American dances of Salsa, Kizomba, Bachata and Rueda. The classes are hosted by the Red Salsa team. L-R: Leigh Nathan, Pat Baloyi, Genevieve Fynn and Saskia De Wet